GitPop: Your Ultimate Git Cheat Sheet

GitPop is a lightweight, easy-to-use Chrome extension that provides instant access to essential Git commands. Whether you're a developer, tester, or just learning Git, GitPop offers a convenient, searchable cheat sheet right within your browser.

Features:
Quick Search: Find Git commands as you type with a fast, responsive search bar.
Efficient Navigation: Automatically scrolls to the relevant command for quick reference.
User-Friendly Design: A clean, minimal interface that fits seamlessly into your workflow.
Stay productive and never lose track of your Git commands with GitPop!
